#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:2
msgid "DNS利用"
msgstr "DNS Exploitation"

#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:5
msgid "DGA"
msgstr "DGA"

#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:6
msgid ""
"DGA（Domain Generate "
"Algorithm，域名生成算法）是一种利用随机字符来生成C&C域名，从而逃避域名黑名单检测的技术手段，常见于botnet中。一般来说，一个DGA域名的存活时间约在1-7天左右。"
msgstr ""
"DGA (Domain Generation Algorithm) is a technique that uses random characters "
"to generate C&C domain names in order to evade domain blacklist detection. It "
"is commonly seen in botnets. In general, a DGA domain name remains active for "
"about 1 to 7 days."

#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:8
msgid "通信时，客户端和服务端都运行同一套DGA算法，生成相同的备选域名列表，当需要发动攻击的时候，选择其中少量进行注册，便可以建立通信，并且可以对注册的域名应用速变IP技术，快速变换IP，从而域名和IP都可以进行快速变化。"
msgstr ""
"During communication, both the client and the server run the same DGA "
"algorithm and generate the same list of candidate domain names. When an "
"attack needs to be launched, registering a small subset of those domains is "
"enough to establish communication. Fast-flux techniques can also be applied "
"to the registered domains to rapidly change IP addresses, allowing both the "
"domain names and IP addresses to change quickly."

#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:10
msgid "DGA域名有多种生成方式，根据种子类型可以分为确定性和不确定性的生成。不确定性的种子可能会选用当天的一些即时数据，如汇率信息等。"
msgstr ""
"DGA domain names can be generated in several ways. Based on the seed type, "
"generation can be deterministic or non-deterministic. Non-deterministic seeds "
"may use time-sensitive data from the current day, such as exchange-rate "
"information."

#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:13
msgid "DNS隧道"
msgstr "DNS Tunneling"

#: ../../source/network/domain/tech.rst:14
msgid "DNS隧道工具将进入隧道的其他协议流量封装到DNS协议内，在隧道上传输。这些数据包出隧道时进行解封装，还原数据。"
msgstr ""
"DNS tunneling tools encapsulate traffic from other protocols into DNS and "
"transmit it through the tunnel. When these packets leave the tunnel, they are "
"decapsulated to restore the original data."
